article_title: YouTube video of Nevada caucus seems to show Hillary supporters voting before registering
article_text:
Voting irregularities benefitting Hillary in a caucus state? Has such a thing ever happened before? Who has ever heard of such a thing? (OK, you can put your hands down....)

That makes this video, posted to YouTube by James Porter and picked up by Kyle Olson of The American Mirror, all too plausible as evidence of fraud.
